title: Looking Back: Our Solo Excursions
description:
In our final throwback of the summer, R&L look back at their first solo excursions back in May 2018, where Link travels to the California Badlands and Rhett gets mistaken for a yoga instructor in a class full of women, on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
